docs.text: Welcome to BOB-otics, Esperanza's Robotics Team For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . What we're all about! mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. Questions? Look up the MKDocs documentation https://www.mkdocs.org/
